\sqrt{1 - \sin{t}} = {\sqrt{1 - \sin{t}}\sqrt{1 + \sin{t}} \over \sqrt{1 + \sin{t}}}
 = {\sqrt{1 - \sin^2(t)} \over \sqrt{1 + \sin(t)}}
= {|\cos(t)| \over \sqrt{1 + \sin(t)}}
2\sqrt{1 + \sin(t)}
-{\pi \over 2} < t < {\pi \over 2}
4\sqrt{2} - 2\sqrt{1 + \sin(t)}
{\pi \over 2} < t < {3\pi \over 2}
